Hey  found a aesome website project euler which is helping me to think mathematically

But yeah i need to find a optimized way for this i found brute force approach

public class Main
{
	public static void main(String[] args) {
	    int k=0,l=0,n=0z=0;
		for(int i=1;i<1000;i++){
		    if(i%3==0){
		        if(i%5==0){
		            z=z+i;
		        }
		        k=k+i;
		    }
		}
		for(int j=1;j<1000;j++){
		    if(j%5==0){
		       l=l+j;
		    }
		}
		
		n=l+k-z;
		System.out.println(n);
	}
}
